---
import { Mail, MessageCircle, Phone } from "@lucide/astro/icons";
---

<section
  id="contacto"
  class="relative isolate min-h-[min(52vh,26rem)] overflow-hidden bg-[#14100f] py-12 sm:min-h-[min(48vh,30rem)] sm:py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-[clamp(4.5rem,9vw,6rem)] lg:pb-[clamp(3.25rem,6vw,4.5rem)]"
>
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/home/cta-bg.png')] bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat sm:bg-[position:center_40%]"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(10,9,8,0.82)_0%,rgba(12,10,9,0.72)_45%,#14100f_100%)]"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_120%_80%_at_50%_0%,rgba(0,0,0,0.35)_0%,transparent_55%)]"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <div
    class="relative z-[1] mx-auto w-full max-w-[1200px] px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"
  >
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[40rem] text-center lg:max-w-[44rem]">
      <h2
        class="mb-4 text-balance text-[clamp(1.35rem,4.2vw,2.75rem)] font-extrabold leading-[1.15] tracking-tight text-white sm:mb-5"
      >
        ¿Tu maquinaria necesita reparación hidráulica?
      </h2>
      <p
        class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-[36rem] text-pretty text-[clamp(0.9375rem,2.1vw,1.125rem)] leading-relaxed text-white/88 sm:mb-10"
      >
        Contáctanos hoy mismo. Reparamos cosechadoras, tractores y todo tipo
        de equipo pesado. También contamos con repuestos hidráulicos
        importados en stock.
      </p>
      <div
        class="mb-8 flex flex-col items-stretch justify-center gap-3 sm:mb-10 sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap sm:items-center sm:gap-4"
      >
        <a
          href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=59170405030&text=¡Hola!%20👋%0A%0AMe%20interesa%20conocer%20más%20sobre%20sus%20servicios%20y%20soluciones%20hidráulicas.%0A%0A¿Podrían%20brindarme%20más%20información?%20Gracias%20🙏"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex min-h-[3rem] items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-secondary px-6 py-3 text-[0.9375rem] font-semibold text-white shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(225,51,44,0.35)] transition duration-300 hover:bg-secondary-dark hover:shadow-[0_6px_24px_rgba(225,51,44,0.45)] sm:min-h-0 sm:px-8 sm:py-3.5 sm:text-base [&_svg]:size-[1.125rem] sm:[&_svg]:size-6 motion-safe:hover:-translate-y-0.5 motion-safe:hover:scale-[1.02] motion-reduce:transition-none"
        >
          <MessageCircle aria-hidden="true" />
          Contactar por WhatsApp
        </a>
        <a
          href="mailto:hydraulicssistem@gmail.com"
          class="inline-flex min-h-[3rem] items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg border-2 border-white/85 bg-white/5 px-6 py-3 text-[0.9375rem] font-semibold text-white backdrop-blur-[2px] transition duration-300 hover:border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-[#1a1513] sm:min-h-0 sm:px-8 sm:py-3.5 sm:text-base [&_svg]:size-[1.125rem] sm:[&_svg]:size-6 motion-safe:hover:-translate-y-0.5 motion-safe:hover:scale-[1.02] motion-reduce:transition-none"
        >
          <Mail aria-hidden="true" />
          Enviar email
        </a>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 text-left text-[0.8125rem] text-white/85 sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap sm:gap-x-10 sm:gap-y-3 sm:text-center sm:text-[0.9375rem]"
      >
        <div
          class="flex w-full max-w-[20rem] items-center justify-start gap-3 sm:w-auto sm:max-w-none sm:justify-center"
        >
          <Phone
            aria-hidden="true"
            class="size-[1.125rem] shrink-0 stroke-[2] text-secondary sm:size-5"
          />
          <a
            href="tel:+59170405030"
            class="font-medium text-white/95 no-underline transition hover:text-secondary"
            >+591 70405030</a
          >
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex w-full max-w-[20rem] items-center justify-start gap-3 sm:w-auto sm:max-w-none sm:justify-center"
        >
          <Mail
            aria-hidden="true"
            class="size-[1.125rem] shrink-0 stroke-[2] text-secondary sm:size-5"
          />
          <a
            href="mailto:hydraulicssistem@gmail.com"
            class="min-w-0 break-all font-medium text-white/95 no-underline transition hover:text-secondary sm:break-normal"
            >hydraulicssistem@gmail.com</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
